y-article-magazine/.highlight/a-major-wave-of-liberal-immigration-has-hit-israel-courtesy-of-vladimir-putin/00000190-eb4f-d8b8-a59a-efdfa4700000</guid></item><item><title>亚特兰蒂斯号失落：以色列军队淹没加沙地下哈马斯隧道网络的计划如何失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/atlantis-is-lost-how-the-israeli-armys-plan-to-flood-hamas-gaza-tunnels-failed/00000190-eb3c-d469-a39d-efbfa7ce0000</link><description>以色列一开始采用了一项陈旧且不合适的计划，随后无视专业建议和被绑架者可能面临的危险，几个月后悄然结束，有人说它是否取得了任何成果。 《国土报》的调查概述了亚特兰蒂斯计划——这是一个可预见的军事失败，直到为时已晚，没有人停止</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 22:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article/.premium/atlantis-is-lost-how-the-israeli-armys-plan-to-flood-hamas-gaza-tunnels-failed/00000190-eb3c-d469-a39d-efbfa7ce0000</guid></item><item><title>他们做了数学计算：希伯来大学伟大的数学家即将离开以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-did-the-math-hebrew-universitys-great-mathematicians-are-leaving-israel/00000190-ebc4-d469-a39d-efd7e73f0000</link><description>在内塔尼亚胡政府的司法改革和加沙无休止的战争的背景下，著名的爱因斯坦数学研究所的七名高级讲师即将离职。趋势是否明显取决于几个变量</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 22:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/they-did-the-math-hebrew-universitys-great-mathematicians-are-leaving-israel/00000190-ebc4-d469-a39d-efd7e73f0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙实地的第一人称现实：“任何进一步的拖延都可能让我们丧命”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/any-delay-could-cost-us-our-lives-reality-on-the-ground-in-gaza-told-in-first-person/00000190-e529-d469-a39d-e5bfdc2a0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦小说家兼文化部长阿特夫·阿布·赛义夫 (Atef Abu Saif) 了解了客厅的哪一部分对于以色列炸弹最安全的感觉。他的新书现已有 13 种语言版本</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 21:08:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/any-delay-could-cost-us-our-lives-reality-on-the-ground-in-gaza-told-in-first-person/00000190-e529-d469-a39d-e5bfdc2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列指责伊朗泄露以色列奥运代表队的详细信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-charges-iran-with-leaked-details-of-israeli-olympic-team/00000190-eb3e-d469-a39d-efbff5740000</link><description>以色列外交部长以色列卡茨警告法国外长，伊朗可能支持针对巴黎的以色列运动员和游客的阴谋</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 20:42:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-charges-iran-with-leaked-details-of-israeli-olympic-team/00000190-eb3e-d469-a39d-efbff5740000</guid></item><item><title>一位定居者解决以色列最大问题的办法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/one-settlers-solution-for-israels-biggest-problems/00000190-e99c-d603-abb5-f99f48c00000</link><description>熔炉理念并不民主，异质社会必须承认多样性。来自埃弗拉特定居点的犹太复国主义者为河流和海洋之间的每个人提供了一些新的价值观</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 20:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/one-settlers-solution-for-israels-biggest-problems/00000190-e99c-d603-abb5-f99f48c00000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列在约旦河西岸建立了25个新的非法哨所</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-erected-25-new-illegal-outposts-in-west-bank-since-gaza-war-started/00000190-eb35-d298-a592-fb375f200000</link><description>非政府组织“立即和平”的一份新报告分析了以色列政府旨在深化吞并进程的各种行动，例如提前批准 8,721 个新住房单元并将约 9.3 平方英里划为国有土地</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:55:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-erected-25-new-illegal-outposts-in-west-bank-since-gaza-war-started/00000190-eb35-d298-a592-fb375f200000</guid></item><item><title>认识在巴黎争夺金牌的以色列奥运奖牌希望者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/meet-israels-olympic-medal-hopefuls-going-for-the-gold-in-paris/00000190-e9e2-d469-a39d-edf70d290000</link><description>艺术体操运动员 Artem Dolgopyat、艺术体操队、风帆冲浪运动员 Sharon Kantor 以及柔道运动员 Raz Hershko 和 Inbar Lanir 都是各自运动领域的佼佼者。但我们不要忘记黑马</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:53:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/meet-israels-olympic-medal-hopefuls-going-for-the-gold-in-paris/00000190-e9e2-d469-a39d-edf70d290000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷与巴比伦之间的航行：结束与开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/navigating-between-jerusalem-babylon-an-end-and-a-beginning/00000190-eabe-d45d-a5b3-ebbe6ec90000</link><description>现在不是结束《国土报》关于犹太人身份的专栏长达 17 年的好时机 — — 尤其是当人们如此不愿意谈论宗教在加沙战争中的作用时。但有一些东西我希望你能带走</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:37:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/navigating-between-jerusalem-babylon-an-end-and-a-beginning/00000190-eabe-d45d-a5b3-ebbe6ec90000</guid></item><item><title>人质家庭敦促以色列军队公布哈马斯在加沙扣押的亲属的照片和其他材料</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-pressing-idf-to-release-photos-other-material-of-kin-held-in-gaza/00000190-eb01-d32c-af96-fbe566ac0000</link><description>最近，一些家庭公开了从军队获得的照片和视频，以加大对政府签署人质协议的压力。军队已移交了家属要求的大部分材料，但仍持有数十张尚未要求的图片、视频和录音</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:16:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/hostage-families-pressing-idf-to-release-photos-other-material-of-kin-held-in-gaza/00000190-eb01-d32c-af96-fbe566ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，以色列士兵在加沙南部可能因吸入有毒气体而死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-due-to-possible-poisonous-gas-inhalation-idf-says/00000190-eb44-d298-a592-fb775a740000</link><description>参谋军士。军方称，诺姆·杜克于周四被杀，可能是吸入发电机中的有毒气体所致。另外两名士兵在同一事件中受重伤，被送往医院接受治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 19:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-due-to-possible-poisonous-gas-inhalation-idf-says/00000190-eb44-d298-a592-fb775a740000</guid></item><item><title>关于以色列发现的高致命病原体您需要了解的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-highly-lethal-pathogen-discovered-in-israel/00000190-eae2-d32c-af96-fbe6313c0000</link><description>什么是福氏耐格里阿米巴原虫，它是如何运作的以及是否可以保护自己免受感染？以色列北部最近发生病例后的综合指南</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 18:50:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/everything-you-need-to-know-about-the-highly-lethal-pathogen-discovered-in-israel/00000190-eae2-d32c-af96-fbe6313c0000</guid></item><item><title>现在分散在以色列各地的独特的北方会众在战时还能保持在一起吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-a-unique-northern-congregation-scattered-across-israel-during-wartime-stay-together/00000190-e077-d9bf-a195-e5ff25500000</link><description>北部城市什莫纳 (Kiryat Shmona) 的进步犹太社区 Poteach Shearim 的成员被迫于 10 月逃离家园。 “一切都是挑战，”拉比奥里特·罗森布利特 (Rabbi Orit Rozenblit) 在过去几个月中说道，但她并不打算放弃她花了数年时间建设的社区</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 18:29:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-a-unique-northern-congregation-scattered-across-israel-during-wartime-stay-together/00000190-e077-d9bf-a195-e5ff25500000</guid></item><item><title>“是时候结束战争了”：内塔尼亚胡和拜登会面时，白宫表示人质协议比以往任何时候都更接近</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-biden-at-white-house-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-eaec-d45d-a5b3-ebeed9260000</link><description>人质家属预计将出席白宫会议。除了释放人质的努力外，美国还寻求内塔尼亚胡关于停止战斗和加沙战后计划的最新信息。内塔尼亚胡周五还将在特朗普位于佛罗里达州的庄园会见特朗普</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 17:25:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-meets-biden-at-white-house-amid-mounting-u-s-pressure-to-end-gaza-war/00000190-eaec-d45d-a5b3-ebeed9260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 293 天：美国高级官员表示，停战谈判似乎已进入最后阶段</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-293-truce-talks-appear-to-be-in-closing-stages-u-s-official-says/00000190-ead6-dd5f-af93-fbd686580000</link><description>据报道，美国、以色列和阿拉伯国家的官员支持任命前巴勒斯坦权力机构安全局长穆罕默德·达赫兰在战后管理加沙 ■ 英国预计将放弃对国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令的要求的保留 ■ 澳大利亚因参与暴力而制裁七名以色列人在约旦河西岸针对巴勒斯坦人 ■ 战争进入 293 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 17:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-293-truce-talks-appear-to-be-in-closing-stages-u-s-official-says/00000190-ead6-dd5f-af93-fbd686580000</guid></item><item><title>与内塔尼亚胡会面前一天，特朗普表示以色列需要“快速”结束加沙战争，夺回人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/day-before-meeting-netanyahu-trump-says-israel-needs-to-end-war-fast-get-hostages-back/00000190-ea5f-d469-a39d-eedf17740000</link><description>这位前总统还批评了那些抗议以色列总理在美国国会演讲的人，呼吁以亵渎美国国旗的罪名判处一年监禁</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/day-before-meeting-netanyahu-trump-says-israel-needs-to-end-war-fast-get-hostages-back/00000190-ea5f-d469-a39d-eedf17740000</guid></item><item><title>利伯曼说，拒绝加入以色列军队的极端正统派应该获得犯罪记录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/mk-lieberman-says-haredim-who-refuse-to-join-idf-should-get-criminal-record/00000190-ea52-dd5f-af93-fb52741b0000</link><description>以色列前国防部长阿维格多·利伯曼表示，“一名真正的正统派士兵——而不是冒充正统派的人——在以色列国防军服役是没有问题的。”他认为，极端正统派可以留在自己的社区内，同时接受世俗教育或征兵。到军队</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 15:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/mk-lieberman-says-haredim-who-refuse-to-join-idf-should-get-criminal-record/00000190-ea52-dd5f-af93-fb52741b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部警方延长对被控杀害 6 岁儿子的妇女的拘留期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/police-extend-detention-for-woman-accused-of-killing-6-year-old-son-in-central-israel/00000190-ea0a-d603-abb5-fb8b22d20000</link><description>上周，嫌疑人在一家商场袭击并打伤一名保安后被捕。几个小时后，她儿子的祖母在家里的公寓里发现了他的尸体，上面有暴力痕迹。邻居过去曾就她的行为向警方报告过</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 14:41:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-25/ty-article/.premium/police-extend-detention-for-woman-accused-of-killing-6-year-old-son-in-central-israel/00000190-ea0a-d603-abb5-fb8b22d20000</guid></item></channel></rss>